<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n12173b"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n12" href="#n12173b">N12 (VI.B.14)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n12all.htm#n12173b"> 173(b)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> pearlies (coster) </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: Pearlies: clothes worn by London costermongers, studded with countless pearl buttons; also the pearl buttons themselves; by extension the leading costermongers, known as the Pearly King and Queen. </mm> </dd></dl>
